question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Var ligger Gyeongju City Hall i Gyeongju, Sydkorea?
answer: Gyeongju City Hall ligger i centrala Gyeongju, i stadsdelen Dongcheon-dong.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located in the centre of Gyeongju, in the Dongcheon-dong district.
